​INTRODUCTION
1. Definitions.
"Platform" shall mean the platform we provide whereby you have access to the Secret Society, whether through our mobile application, through our website or through any other device through which you are able to access our platform.
"Member" shall mean a social media influencer, socialite, celebrity, model, promotor, presenter or otherwise influential person accepted by the Secret Society and provided with an account for the purpose of being eligible to avail Promotions (defined below).
"Service Provider" shall mean any designer, venue, events company, brand, service provider, owner of products or otherwise, accepted by the Secret Society to provide Promotions to be availed by Members.
"Promotion" or "Promotions" shall mean any event, product, service or otherwise which the Service Provider wishes to be availed by a Member in accordance with these Terms and Conditions below.
