META/FACEBOOK
We use Facebook data to streamline collaborations. You can delete your account at any time requesting it to
support@the-secret-society.com
. Complete deletion will be done within a month.
1. Data Deletion Requests
Users can request data deletion via both the mobile app and web platform. Once a request is received, the process will take up to 2 weeks to complete. During this period, data will be anonymized, effectively removing personal identifiers.
2. Data Processing Details
We process the following data:
Facebook Insights: Used to enhance user experience by providing insights related to user activity.
Birthdate: Required to verify age eligibility for certain events. Please note that once provided, the birthdate cannot be updated by users.
Facebook Pages: Utilized to establish a connection between Instagram Insights and our platform.
First and Last Name: Collected to pre-fill the registration form and facilitate user identification on the manager side when users are invited to events. Users can manually update their name during registration.
3. Purpose of Data Processing
Facebook Insights: To offer a more personalized and improved user experience.
Birthdate: Ensures compliance with age restrictions for specific events.
First and Last Name: Streamlines the registration process and allows managers to accurately identify users during event invitations.
